<P>This is brought but as a parallel Ca&s;e,
for upon Examination no Treachery was
found in the $a&s;e at all, but the <HI>Eng|li&s;h</HI>
Admiral thought the Inequality too
great to venture a general Engagement;
likewife in this Ca&s;e we may be ju&s;tly &s;aid
to be Unea&s;ie, and not think our&s;elves Safe,
while $i&s;under&s;tandings and Jealou&s;ies are
