<P>Now Her Maje&s;ty di&s;appointed them
All by coming to this Happy Re&s;olu|tion,
(<HI>viz.</HI>) &startq;If ye will not treat of Peace,
neither will I carry on the War; if all
that can be expected by the War may
be obtained by a Treaty of Peace, I
cannot &s;atisfie my&s;elf to let any more
Blood be &s;hed when it may upon &s;o good
